People’s Daily commentator: Concentrate on doing your own affairs well and create new advantages for future development-on studying and implementing General Secretary Xi Jinping’s important speech at the entrepreneurs forum-Xinhua
Xinhua News Agency, Beijing, July 25th. People’s Daily, July 26th Commentator’s article: Concentrate on doing your own affairs and create new advantages for future development
At present, the global epidemic situation and the world economic situation are still severe and complex, and the challenges facing my country’s development are unprecedented.
Maintaining strategic determination, enhancing confidence in victory, and concentrating our efforts on doing our own affairs are the keys to our response to various risks and challenges.
At the recent entrepreneurs forum, General Secretary Xi Jinping emphasized that in the current external environment of rising protectionism, downturn in the world economy, and shrinking global markets, we must concentrate our efforts on our own affairs and give full play to the advantages of the domestic super-large-scale market. , Gradually form a new development pattern with the domestic cycle as the main body and the domestic and international dual cycles mutually promoting each other, improve the modernization level of the industrial chain and supply chain, vigorously promote scientific and technological innovation, accelerate the research on key core technologies, and create new advantages for future development.
Those who observe the situation are wise, and those who control the situation win.
In the external environment of the in-depth development of economic globalization, the “two ends” of the market and resources have played an important role in the rapid development of our country.
Now, the world under the impact of the epidemic is undergoing profound changes, facing more unstable and uncertain factors, and economic globalization is encountering headwinds and waves of backlash.
To be prepared for a longer period of time to respond to changes in the external environment, and to promote my country’s economy to ride the winds and waves, stabilize and achieve long-term development, an extremely important aspect is to take the expansion and satisfaction of domestic demand as the strategic basis for development, give full play to its own advantages, and adopt Prospering the domestic economy and unblocking the domestic cycle will add impetus to my country’s economic development and drive the recovery of the world economy.
We must deeply realize that building a complete domestic demand system has a bearing on my country’s long-term development and long-term stability.
