Xinhua News Agency, Kuala Lumpur, July 25 (Reporter Lin Hao) A video conference of APEC trade ministers was held on the 25th. The meeting promised to work to reduce the impact of the COVID-19 on the regional economy and accelerate the realization of flexibility and sustainability And inclusive regional economic recovery.
