chinanews.com, Xiamen, July 26 (Yang Fushan, Zhang Shushan, Xu Jingyi) The Department of Vascular Surgery, Shanghai Changhai Hospital of Naval Military Medical University, China’s famous vascular surgery center, signed a contract with the Department of Vascular Surgery of Zhongshan Hospital Affiliated to Xiamen University on the 25th to establish a collaboration center. Promote exchanges and cooperation between the two parties in the field of vascular surgery, especially in the field of acute and severe aortic diseases.
